0.0.5 Thu Mar 17 09:05:53 CET 2011
	- Show human readable file sizes.
	- Add the flag --db DB, which allows the caller to change the db file.
	- Add the options --md5 and --sha1 and rename --show to --list.
	- Fix OS X compilation warnings.

0.0.4 Sun Apr 25 00:14:28 CEST 2010
	- Add the option --zero which allows empty files to be indexed.
	- Add the last modification time to each file.

0.0.3 Sat Apr 24 14:08:55 CEST 20
	- Fix the usage.
	- autogen.sh is now working in OS X (ports uses a different aclocal folder).

0.0.2 Sat Feb 27 22:32:43 CET 2010
	- Add the option --replace which replaces old digest in the database.
	- Add the option --show which show the digests with duplicates.
	- License under LGPL v. 2.1.

0.0.1 Mon Feb 22 21:56:22 CET 2010
	- Initial release.
